                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220911-320-off1672 t18220911-320-cd1673"></join>, one pistol, value 5 s.; one brush, value 2 s., and one pair of scissors, value 1 s.
            </rs>, the goods of Sir 
