                     <interp inst="t18220911-320-person2829" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was at my brother's residence during his absence on the Continent; I had lent<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182209110129"></xptr>the pistols to the footman; she prisoner was leaving the service.</p>
               <p>ISAAC HAWKINS. I took him in charge, he said he knew nothing of the charge.</p>
